org.bonitasoft.engine.bpm.process

Interface ArchivedProcessInstance

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ArchivedElement, BaseElement, BonitaObject, NamedElement, Serializable

    public interface ArchivedProcessInstance
extends NamedElement, BaseElement, ArchivedElement
    Represents an archived instance of a process. Gives access to the information of the instance, whereas the state, the definition, the archived date of the process instance...
    Since:
    6.0.0
    Version:
    6.3.5
    Author:
    Baptiste Mesta, Elias Ricken de Medeiros, Matthieu Chaffotte, Celine Souchet
